    "description": "A THOUSAND MOUTHS TO SCREAM is a space horror visual novel with interactive point and click elements.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou will observe the life of Nick the only crew member of an intelligent spaceship.<br />\r\nThis ship has everything it needs to keep itself and its crew alive. <br />\r\nThe ship feeds, treats Nick, makes sure he's well.<br />\r\nIt's a choose-your-own-adventure style game. You will have to make choices and see the consequences.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThe interaction with the game is in the spirit of point and click games.<br />\r\nYou can move around the ship, explore its interiors, interact with various objects.<br />\r\nYour actions will affect the ending you get.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nFeatures:<br />\r\n- An interactive point-and-click environment.<br />\r\n- Atmospheric retro graphics.<br />\r\n- A short experience that can be completed in one sitting.<br />\r\n- The game has multiple endings.",
